data.description:
Welcome Home! This updated 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath plus flex space/loft home is located in the highly desirable Seven Oaks neighborhood offers over 2200 square feet of well-designed living space. Some of the attractive features of this property include fresh neutral paint in the main living areas, a newer AC unit (2022), a newer water heater (2023), upgraded light fixtures, updated LVP flooring throughout the entire home, granite countertops in the kitchen, and stainless steel appliances. The powder room and primary bathroom have also been newly remodeled.
In addition to the features of the home, Seven Oaks offers amenities such as a swimming pool, clubhouse available for rent for parties, sidewalks, a playground/picnic area, and a pond where residents can fish. The neighborhood is conveniently located directly across from Reedy Creek Park and is a short drive to i485, i85, and Uptown Charlotte.
This property is a true gem and presents a great opportunity to make it your dream home.
